Title: Construction of trigonometric Toda $r$-matrices via Hamiltonian
  reduction of the cotangent bundle over loop groups
Authors: G.E.Arutyunov
Comments: 10 pages, LATEX
\\
  By applying the Hamiltonian reduction method to the cotangent bundle over
loop groups we recover the well-known classical trigonometric $r$-matrices of
the periodic Toda lattice.
